Sinesis wandered around by a big lake....he looked into the lake to see if
maybe there was somebody there who needed a whipping...then he heard the
whistle.....Sinister appeared again, and was strung up into a
tree!.....Sinesis laughed as his plan worked.... "you fool!.....you fell
into my trap!..." Sinesis said...then, Sinister disenigrated...Sinesis
looked in shock but did not notice the real Sinister come up from behind and
stab him in the back........Sinesis gasped and fell to the ground, falling
off the dagger which was still in the hands of Sinister....Sinesis rolled
over and looked into the eyes of Sinister.....Sinister plunged his knife
toward Sinesis, Sinesis caught it in his hands and was struggling to keep it
up.......Sinister wanted it to come DOWN.....they continued to fight for
hours, both trying to force the knife in opposite directions.....noth not
giving up...... "i shall not give in!.." Sinesis said...... "you never gave
in to guilt when you killed our parents neither, did you?...." sinister
said.... "i didn't kill our parents!....they killed themselves! they were
lunatics!...." sinesis said....Sinister paused...he knew Sinesis wouldn't
lie to him.....he rememberd to oath to never lie..... "you never asked waht
happened that day, you just assumed..." Sinesis said as Sinister's knife
moved away.....after they looked at each other for a while...there was a hug
and a handshake, and the brothers were back together once again..... "we
must first eliminate the threats..." sinister said.... "yes, i shall wrestle
them down to size...." said Sinesis....they walked off in the same
direction, a team once more......
